    "description":  "How training providers can create traineeship vacancies and advertise them on Find a traineeship.",
    "details":  {
                    "attachments":  [

                                    ],
                    "body":  "\u003cdiv class=\"govspeak\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"call-to-action\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFrom 1 August 2023, we will no longer fund a standalone national traineeships programme. Traineeships can continue to be offered as part of our general skills offer.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe last start date for a traineeship is 31 July 2023.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou will be able to submit new vacancies for traineeships until 31 December 2023.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eRead the \u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://questions-statements.parliament.uk/written-statements/detail/2022-12-12/hcws434\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003ewritten ministerial statement on the skills update\u003c/a\u003e from Robert Halfon, Minister for Skills, Apprenticeships and Higher Education.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou can create a traineeship vacancy in the \u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://providers.apprenticeships.education.gov.uk/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003e‘Recruit a trainee’ section of your apprenticeship service account\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eTo create a vacancy, you’ll need to be on the \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/register-of-apprenticeship-training-providers?msclkid=25e851f8aab411ec80be3e24ca00e596\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eRegister of apprenticeship training providers\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou will need the employer to give you permission within their apprenticeship service account to create traineeship vacancies on their behalf.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe usually approve or reject traineeship vacancies within 24 hours.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf you deliver traineeships but don’t deliver apprenticeships, you can work with a provider on the Register of apprenticeship training providers who can deliver an apprenticeship following your traineeship. They can advertise traineeship vacancies for you on Find a traineeship.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eBefore you create a vacancy, learn about \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/employer-preventing-discrimination/recruitment\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003epreventing discrimination in recruitment\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"what-youll-need\"\u003eWhat you’ll need\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eBefore you start, you’ll need to know the:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ename of the traineeship vacancy\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003etraineeship sector\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eemployer that will provide the work experience placement and whether they are disability confident\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eemployer’s address and location\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003enumber of positions available\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003estart date and application closing date\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eduration of the traineeship and details of a typical working week\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou can save each vacancy as a draft and edit it before you submit it to us, as well as preview how it’ll look.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"what-happens-next\"\u003eWhat happens next\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou can check the status of each vacancy in your traineeship dashboard. The statuses are:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003erejected\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003edraft\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003elive\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eclosed\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003epending review\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe’ll check the vacancy and let you know if you need to make any edits within 24 hours. You can view what edits you need to make on your dashboard, but you can also choose to get email notifications.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eOnce we’ve approved the vacancy, you can view it on Find a traineeship.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou can also extend the closing date after the vacancy has gone live.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e",
